edu.iastate.scribbleshare.Frame

Class Frame

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.iastate.scribbleshare.Frame.Frame

  • public class Frame
extends java.lang.Object
    A single frame of a post which holds user comments for that frame. A frame must have a unique, generated ID, a one to many list of Comments posted under it, a backwards pointing, one to one relationship with the post it is under (for easier data manipulation), and an index value. The index must represent the ordering of the frame for a given post
